name: Justin Mixon
description: I am passionate about living life to its fullest! For me that includes travelling to new places and experiencing all sorts of things. There’s nothing quite like exiting an airport in a new country and taking that first breath of air. Every city, let me tell you, has its own smell. Give me a room with a view, and i’m good to go! My own travels have taught me to see my home town through the eyes of a tourist. I now know more about my hometown and make a great tourist guide when friends come to visit.
